	</div>
</div>


<div class="text-block row">
	<div class="large-8 columns large-offset-2">
		<p class="big">
		For me, her story was inspiring, but the premise was terrifying. My eyesight is by far my most precious sense, and I find it hard to imagine how I could adapt.
		</p>
		<br>
		<p class="big">
		I’ve always been in love with images. I started drawing at an early age. (One of my earliest memories is getting into big trouble after painting watercolor "murals" on the apartment walls – right before an open house showing.) In college, I decided to major in Product Design because I liked the idea of bringing utility to something beautiful.
		</p>
		<br>
		<p class="big">
		And now, I’m a designer, working in the interaction + visual design realm. I have a deep interest in understanding user needs and creating tools.
		</p>
	</div>
</div>


